title: Morocco Banks Balance Sheet
description: Banks Balance Sheet in Morocco increased to 1698048 MAD Million in September from 1672865 MAD Million in August of 2022. Banks Balance Sheet in Morocco averaged 958585.01 MAD Million from 2001 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 1698048 MAD Million in September of 2022 and a record low of 360422.93 MAD Million in March of 2002. This page provides - Morocco Banks Balance Sheet - actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Central Bank of Morocco
